<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate")%>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>
          <p class="lead text-center">
            At the forefront of innovation in the aluminum manufacturing
            industry, our mission is to leverage cutting-edge technology to
            enhance efficiency and quality.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our project focuses on developing a machine learning-based solution
            to predict the physical properties of aluminum wire rods, such as
            tensile strength, yield strength, and elongation. By analyzing key
            input parameters, including the percentages of aluminum, magnesium,
            zinc, silicon, temperature, rolling speed, and heat treatment
            status, our model provides manufacturers with precise predictions to
            streamline production.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our team utilizes advanced technologies to build an intuitive,
            user-friendly interface. The frontend, built using EJS, allows users
            to easily input data, while our Node.js backend processes the
            information swiftly, offering real-time predictions. This reduces
            the need for extensive physical testing, saving both time and
            resources.
          </p>

          <p>
            We believe in continuous improvement and have integrated a feedback
            mechanism to refine our model over time, ensuring it adapts to
            evolving manufacturing requirements. Our solution empowers
            manufacturers to make data-driven decisions, optimize production
            processes, and maintain the highest quality standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

